name: Brookhaven Houses Thief Game
description:
Welcome to the brookhaven houses thief game you have to go into the brookhaven house to get some money and jewellery, but watch out there are police everywhere.
You have to pass all stages of the game to become the champion.

- Excellent interface & HD graphics.
- easy to Play brookhaven rp and gangster.
- The game features fast on all devices

Enjoy the game with your family and friends
